{"service_name": "Information Assurance / Security", "service_id": "4992803432038400", "company_name": "Triad Consulting & Solutions", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Triad Consulting &amp; Solutions\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Information Assurance / Security\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Triad's service assists organisations in identifying and meeting their information security and information assurance requirements. Our service includes delivering Information Security Management Systems, developing security policy, establishing governance structures; achieving  ISO27001 certification;  information assurance and accreditation of secure systems; implementation of Government standards and best practice.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Delivery of information security management systems (ISMS)\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Development of security policy\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Establishment of governance structures and operational security processes and procedures\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Assistance in achieving and maintaining ISO27001 certification\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Implement Cabinet Office Information Assurance Standards and Good Practice Guides\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Provision of security requirements analysis service\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Architecture and design services for identity and access management solutions\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Assure your solutions against government guidelines\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Produce technical risk assessments and RMADS\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Conduct IT Health Checks (ITHC)\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     A wealth of experience in information risk management and assurance\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Provision of CLAS consultancy\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Security cleared staff\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Assists in accreditation to ISO27001 and PCI\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Assesses your solutions against threats and vulnerabilities\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Provides guidance to define your security policy\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Development of cloud based security policy\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Enhanced and assured information security\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     We will work collaboratively with you, at your offices\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3650 to \u00a3850 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Hour\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92382/4992803432038400-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92382/4992803432038400-sfia-rate-card.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-